{"article_id":"sa1NlCc9iSO6mM91","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Mitt Romney 's campaign raises over $ 2.5 million in hours after the ruling","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Complex","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"ruling a victory for the White House ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"may also energize Republican base","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"GOP will grab onto view of new `` tax ''","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"and use it","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"to attack President Barack Obama","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"The U.S. Supreme Court 's narrow upholding of the health care reform law now launches a complex political ballet ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"with President Barack Obama and Democrats claiming victory","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"and Republicans immediately seizing on the word `` tax , '' vowing to repeal the law `` lock , stock and barrel . ''","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"In a 5-4 decision , the court upheld the law","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"and found","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"that the so-called individual mandate is constitutional under Congress ' taxing power","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"but not under the commerce clause of the Constitution ,","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"as the government originally had argued .","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"Republicans","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"-- including presidential candidate Mitt Romney --","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"claimed","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"the mandate should be seen as a tax increase .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Obama had previously rejected the idea","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"that the mandate amounts to a tax .","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"Romney lashed out at the ruling and the president ,","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"claiming","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"the law 's provisions","depth":14},{"id":25,"text":"to impose a penalty on those","depth":15},{"id":26,"text":"who are n't insured","depth":15},{"id":27,"text":"amounts to a tax increase .","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"Other parts of the law require individuals","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"making more than $ 200,000","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"to pay more into Medicare","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"and imposes an excise tax on high-cost employer health insurance plans","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"if their plan cost tops $ 10,200 for individual coverage and $ 27,500 for family coverage . `` Obamacare raises taxes on the American people by approximately $ 500 billion , ''","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"Romney said Thursday .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"Chief Justice John Roberts clarified the tax issue in his opinion :","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"`` The Federal Government does not have the power","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"to order people to buy health insurance .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"( It ) would therefore be unconstitutional","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"if read as a command .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"The Federal Government does have the power","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"to impose a tax on those","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"without health insurance .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"( It ) is therefore constitutional ,","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"because it can reasonably be read as a tax . ''","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"`` Here 's the bottom line now , ''","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"said Sen. Marco Rubio , R-Fla.","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"`` It is constitutional","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"according to the Supreme Court","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"because it is a tax increase ...","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"now millions of Americans will have an IRS problem","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"beginning in 2014 . ''","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Republicans likely will use the tax argument as a battle cry on the campaign trail","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"as Romney quickly repeated his vow","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"to repeal the law","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"if he is elected president .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"`` What the court did not do on its last day of session , I will do on my first day","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"if I am elected president of the United States , ''","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"Romney said Thursday .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"`` I will act","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"to repeal Obamacare . ''","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"For his part , Obama sees his role in the protracted saga as that of a leader","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"willing to take a politically unpopular stand on health care .","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"Romney :","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"I 'll do what justices did n't","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Romney :","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"I 'll do what justices did n't","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"04:11","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Ruling on individual mandate explained","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"Ruling on individual mandate explained","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"01:49","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"How will the court 's ruling affect you ?","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"How will the court 's ruling affect you ?","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"02:14","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"`` I did n't do this","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"because it 's good politics .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"I did it","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"because I believed","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"it was good for the country .","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"I did it","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"because I believed","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"it was good for the American people , ''","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"Obama said .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"Later Thursday , in a memo from Democratic officials , the Obama re-election campaign added :","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"`` All three branches of government have now agreed","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"that President Obama 's health care law is the right thing","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"to do ...","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"It 's time","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"to move past the same political battles","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"and fully implement the law . ''","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"Both sides will now take their case to the American electorate","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"heading into the fall election .","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"On Capitol Hill , Republicans","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"who fought hard against the law 's initial passage","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"were not happy .","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"`` The president of the United States himself , promised up and down","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"that this bill was not a tax , ''","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Mitch McConnell said from the Senate floor .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"`` This is one of the Democrats ' top selling points","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"because they knew","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"it would not pass","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"if it was a tax .","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"Well , the Supreme Court has spoken","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"--","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"this law is a tax .","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"The bill was sold to the American people on a deception . ''","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"House Speaker John Boehner , R-Ohio , was more blunt .","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"`` The government could decide","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"that we are going to tax you","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"if you do n't eat broccoli on Tuesday , ''","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"Boehner said .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"`` Apparently now that is constitutional ,","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"but I do n't think","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"it is a very wise law . ''","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"House Majority Leader Eric Cantor , R-Virginia said","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"he was `` disappointed '' in the decision and on his way into a closed door House GOP meeting on the ruling .","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"the House will vote","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"after it returns from July Fourth recess","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"to repeal the health care law .","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"A visibly relieved Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid , D-Nevada , applauded the decision from the Senate floor .","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"Like Obama , the veteran lawmaker spent enormous political capital","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"marshaling his caucus","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"and pushing the law 's passage .","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"`` Passing the Affordable Care Act was the greatest single step in generations","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"toward ensuring access to affordable , quality health care for every person in America","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"regardless of where they live , how much they make , ''","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"Reid said Thursday .","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"The key House leader","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"who pushed through the bill in 2010","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"indicated","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"the court 's ruling was a vindication of months of work .","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"`` In passing health reform ,","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"we made history for our nation and progress for the American people .","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"We completed the unfinished business of our society","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"and strengthened the character of our country , ''","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"said House Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi , D-California ,","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"who was House speaker","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"until her party lost the majority in the 2010 midterm elections .","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"`` We ensured","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"health care would be a right for all , not a privilege for the few .","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"Today , the Supreme Court affirmed our progress","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"and protected that right ,","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"securing a future of health and economic security for the middle class and for every American . ''","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"And the ruling was a much-needed win for a president","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"locked in a tough re-election campaign .","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"`` It is a major part of the president 's potential legacy , ''","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"said Andrew Rudalevige , an associate political science professor at Dickinson College and author of `` The New Imperial Presidency :","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"Renewing Presidential Power After Watergate . ''","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"`` And the individual mandate does hold the substance of the package together , costwise and substantively . ''","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"When Obama signed the Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act into law in 2010 ,","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"the move heralded a major","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"-- albeit hard-won --","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"political victory for the president .","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"The controversial legislation ,","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"which critics dubbed `` Obamacare , ''","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"extended coverage to 30 million Americans","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"and was the culmination of a drawn-out and deeply partisan fight about the role of government .","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"For Obama , the law 's passage proved his administration 's ability","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"to push through its policy agenda","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"despite strong oppositional headwinds .","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"As Vice President Joe Biden told Obama","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"after the law passed :","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"`` This is a big f -- -ing deal . ''","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"But netting that deal also cost the president tremendous political capital .","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"During the August recess of 2009 , angry conservatives stormed congressional town halls","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"to protest the legislation .","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"Repeal `` Obamacare '' became the rallying cry for a new wave of tea party-backed Republican House freshmen .","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"Their massive sweep during the 2010 elections sent moderate Democrats packing","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"and flipped control of the House of Representatives to the GOP .","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"Within months of the law 's passage , the controversial law was in the courts .","depth":7},{"id":179,"text":"Conflicting appellate rulings ultimately led to the case being sent to the U.S. Supreme Court .","depth":8},{"id":180,"text":"Twenty-six states also pressed the Supreme Court to examine the law .","depth":8},{"id":181,"text":"Since the law was modeled after a similar Massachusetts measure ,","depth":8},{"id":182,"text":"as the state 's former governor , Romney , will face heightened scrutiny from conservatives","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"determined to hold him to his campaign promises","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"to repeal the law .","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"there 's an upside for the president here , ''","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"said Ilya Shapiro , a senior fellow at the Libertarian-leaning Cato Institute and an expert on the Supreme Court .","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"The ruling `` energizes Republicans and the tea party . ''","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"Rudalevige added ,","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"`` Romney will of course try to tie Obama back to the issue . ''","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"And Romney will have support from the Republican National Committee ,","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"which launched the website `` PeopleVObamaCare.com '' after the court 's decision .","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"Romney press secretary Andrea Saul tweeted","depth":9},{"id":194,"text":"that in the hours after the ruling , the campaign raised $ 2.5 million online from more than 24,000 donors","depth":10},{"id":195,"text":"-- touting a hashtag , # FullRepeal ,","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"set up","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"to promote their effort","depth":13},{"id":198,"text":"to overturn the law .","depth":13},{"id":199,"text":"Reflecting after the ruling ,","depth":6},{"id":200,"text":"Pelosi recalled the longtime dream of Sen. Ted Kennedy , a longtime champion of health care reform","depth":7},{"id":201,"text":"who died in 2009 , a year before the legislation 's passage .","depth":7},{"id":202,"text":"`` I knew","depth":9},{"id":203,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":204,"text":"when he left us","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"he would go to heaven","depth":12},{"id":206,"text":"and help pass the bill , ''","depth":11},{"id":207,"text":"she said from Capitol Hill .","depth":8},{"id":208,"text":"`` And now he can rest in peace .","depth":7},{"id":209,"text":"His dream for America 's families has become a reality . ''","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":419,"left":217,"right":418,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":217,"left":211,"right":216,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":216,"left":2,"right":215,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":215,"left":212,"right":214,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":214,"left":5,"right":213,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":213,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":418,"left":308,"right":417,"relation":